OL,5,G1100 The Straight Story
OL,6,     F(1999) David Lynch's fact-based
OL,7,     Fdrama with Richard Farnsworth.
OL,8,     FAlvin Straight drives hundreds of
OL,9,     Fmiles across the USA on a
OL,10,     Flawnmower to visit his dying
OL,11,     Fbrother - Harry Dean Stanton.
OL,12,G1315 The Guns of Fort Petticoat
OL,13,     F(1957) Western. A Union army
OL,14,     Fdeserter sets out to turn his
OL,15,     FTexan hometown's womenfolk into
OL,16,     Fsharpshooters in order to repel a
OL,17,     FComanche attack. Starring Audie
OL,18,     FMurphy and Kathryn Grant.
